<br>
lvl 1 - Shallow Breath - Single Target Magical Direct Damage with Debuff (Max: 5)<br>
<br>
lvl 4 - Suffocating Sphere - Single Target Magical Direct Damage with Debuff (Max: 10)<br>
<br>
lvl 12 - Choke - Single Target Magical Debuff DoT (Max: 80)<br>
<br>
