<br>
As a high elf Enchantress I solo'd until level 16 because I could never get a group before that. Until I got level 16 I pretty much stayed in the faydark continent. If you are level 10 now you can probably go to steamfont hills and kill the skeletons there or even some elementals and other things. You will of course need to be really careful because things can get out of hand pretty fast when they start to run away.<br>
<br>
At level 16 you can go to Lake of ill omen (you will want to go to FV anyways to get your first mana regen spell &quot;breeze&quot;) and fight at the mill area. I would suggest grouping also as an enchanting class. My experiences have found grouping in dungeons to be far more enjoyable for myself than grouping outside or solo'ing. =)<br>
<br>
